description:
You’ll love my place because of the coziness. My place is good for solo adventurers and business travelers. Minimal. Furnished Cozy studio in upper Harlem. Great for Holiday travelers and students. 

Features: Kitchen with stove, gas, electric and fridge. Full bathroom.
name: Furnished Cozy Studio in Central Harlem
review: Near train station and easy to get to Time sq. but the area is a bit desolate and somewhat scary. Host is accommodating. Apartment is clean.
